143. Can constructors be inherited?

Not directly. But parent constructor is called automatically if child does not define __init__() or via super().

144. Can static methods be overridden?

Yes. But it is not true polymorphism; it behaves like method hiding.

145. Can instance methods access static variables?

Yes. Instance methods can access static variables using class name or object.

146. Can static methods access instance variables?

No. Static methods cannot access instance variables directly.

147. Can class methods access instance variables?

No. Class methods can access only class variables via cls.

148. Can instance methods access class variables?

Yes. Instance methods can access class variables.

